Package: quanyu
Title: Interactive Bushfire Analytics in SE Australia: FWI-MSR & Burned Area
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Quanyu", family = "Qian",
           email = "qqia0010@student.monash.edu",
           role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Provides cleaned ERA5-derived fire weather metrics (FWI and MSR) and
    MODIS burned area summaries for southeastern Australia, together with a Shiny
    app for interactive exploration of their relationships and a vignette that
    documents the data processing steps used in prior ETC5523 assignments.
